==================
Installation Notes
==================
This version is tested on Ubuntu 16.04 and 18.04 (x_86 64 bit architecture).
It required python and perl to be installed on the system

1. untar the archive into <mydcvalid> directory
2. set an environment variable 
export DCVALID_CONFIG_PATH=<path to mydcvalid directory>
export PATH=$DCVALID_CONFIG_PATH/bin:$PATH

Better to add it to .bashrc file.
You will be able to use following command
dcvalid <dc file>
